{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"Seletores de classe","mdn_url":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/CSS/Class_selectors","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p>O <strong>seletor de classes</strong> <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/CSS\">CSS</a> corresponde aos elementos com base no conteúdo de seus atributos <code>class.</code></p>\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: css notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token comment\">/* Todos os elementos com class=\"espaçoso\" */</span>\n<span class=\"token selector\">.espaçoso</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">margin</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 2em<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">/* Todos os elementos &lt;li&gt; com class=\"espaçoso\" */</span>\n<span class=\"token selector\">li.espaçoso</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">margin</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 2em<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">/* Todos os elementos &lt;li&gt; cujo conteúdo do atributo class possua \"espaçoso\" e \"elegante\" */</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">/* Por exemplo, class=\"elegante antigo espaçoso\" */</span>\n<span class=\"token selector\">li.espaçoso.elegante</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">margin</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 2em<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"sintaxe","title":"Sintaxe","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"notranslate\">.classe_nome { propriedades de estilo }\n</pre>\n<p>Observe que isso é o mesmo que <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/Attribute_selectors\"><code>seletor de atributo</code></a>:</p>\n<pre class=\"notranslate\">[classe~=classe_nome] { propriedades de estilo  }\n</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"exemplo","title":"Exemplo","isH3":false,"content":""}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"css","title":"CSS","isH3":true,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: css notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token selector\">.vermelho</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> #f33<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"token selector\">.amarelo-bg</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">background</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> #ffa<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"token selector\">.elegante</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">font-weight</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> bold<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">text-shadow</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 4px 4px 3px #77f<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"html","title":"HTML","isH3":true,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: html notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>p</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">class</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>vermelho<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>Este parágrafo tem o texto vermelho.<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>p</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">class</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>vermelho amarelo-bg<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>Este parágrafo possui texto em vermelho e fundo amarelo.<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>p</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">class</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>vermelho elegante<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>Este parágrafo possui texto em vermelho e uma propriedade de estilo \"elegante\".<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>Este é um parágrafo comum.<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"resultado","title":"Resultado","isH3":true,"content":"<iframe class=\"sample-code-frame\" title=\"Exemplo\" id=\"frame_example\" src=\"https://yari-demos.prod.mdn.mozit.cloud/pt-BR/do